{
  "stem": "24651.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father returned to Nowy Targ.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he and his brothers and father joined the Polish army, if there was such a thing, and tried to repel the Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Apparently, the Polish army disbanded very shortly and they just came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that point, my father and his brothers [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] joined this caravan of people heading eastward.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandmother and my grandfather and one uncle remained.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They chose not to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father finally arrived in Russia, but he could-- he didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were separated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father said-- so my father was in Lvov.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were in a town called [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wutsk. ?] I don't think that was terribly far from-- the two towns were close by.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father advertised in the newspaper looking for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He mentioned me-- he particularly mentioned that I had a birthmark on my leg, and so he mentioned that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in time, he did find us and joined us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, at that point, my father and my grandfather and all the men had to think of a way of earning a living.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they decided to take dairy products from the country, bring it to the city, and that's how they earned some money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all lived together in one big-- it wasn't so big, but one ar-- one house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after a while, my father and my mother and I and my sister left them, because we were just too crowded.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went to a town called Winniki.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that point, my father got a job working in a coke-- like a peat factory, you know, for coal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so that's what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
